{
  "stem": "11133.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It had taken them a while to accumulate these things, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it just-- life just changed, completely, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You lost your sense-- not that you ever had a tremendous sense of security, but as a child, I did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at that point, I no longer had that sense of security.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was totally replaced by the beginnings of fear, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember my-- my father worked for a-- he was an accountant in a shirt factory named HoGo.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think, the initials stood for Horowitz and Goldfarb, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was sort of analogous to Arrow factory, Arrow Shirt, a Manhattan, here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he got one of the maintenance men there to come with a push cart-- you know that they used to carry the shirts from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we loaded up some of our personal belongings, and we moved-- I mean, we didn't-- a few sticks of furniture, like mattresses and beds.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we moved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Books, probably.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And maybe some dolls.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was very fond of dolls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We moved to-- well, they moved us-- the ghetto then became-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they moved us into what used to be the Jewish section of town.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, actually, they moved us twice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, the ghetto kept shrinking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at first, it was much larger, and then it shrank some more and shrank some more.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they started breaking us up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they-- at first, we didn't have any walls around the ghetto, but then they started putting up a wall around the ghetto, and they even bricked in windows and doors, you know, of buildings facing towards the outside of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
